    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust BMW E46 M3, a quintessential analog driver\u2019s machine. At its heart is the S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a recently serviced double-VANOS system for peak high-RPM performance. The power is managed by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a functional limited-slip differential. This example has undergone proactive maintenance, including subframe inspection and suspension bushing refreshes, ensuring the chassis handles with factory-spec rigidity. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain is dialed in and ready for the apex. Features staggered Style 67 alloys and a crisp, responsive hydraulic steering rack.",
